Interface PwAdLoader.PwAdLoaderListener<T>

  • Enclosing class:
    PwAdLoader<T>

    public static interface PwAdLoader.PwAdLoaderListener<T>
    Implement this interface to be notified of ad loading events.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onFail(PwAdLoader loader, String error)
      This event is fired if there was an error retrieving the ads.

      • onFail

        void onFail(PwAdLoader loader,
            String error)
        This event is fired if there was an error retrieving the ads.
        Parameters:
        loader - the loader that requested the ads
        error - description of the error that occurred. The error messages are intended to provide information for developers and should not be displayed to the user.
